Parliament, Monday, 16 September 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Tourism will tomorrow consider the draft Concept Paper on Tourism Oversight Forum, and the draft Committee Programme for the Third Term of 2019. There will also be an update on the preparations for World Tourism Celebrations. Date: Tuesday, 17 September 2019
	Time: 10:00-12:45
	Venue: Committee Room E340, Third Floor, National Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON TOURISM, MR SUPRA MAHUMAPELO. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Sureshinee Govender
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 2239
	Cell: 081 704 1109
